1632_HTTP_Telegram_Monitor_Webhook.description_en: This n8n workflow template allows users to check if a Tron wallet address is blacklisted on the USDT contract via a Telegram bot. When a user sends the command {walletAddress} through the Telegram bot, the workflow queries the Tronscan API to determine if the provided wallet address is blacklisted. The result is then sent back to the user via the Telegram bot.
1632_HTTP_Telegram_Monitor_Webhook.description_zh: 此 n8n 工作流模板允许用户通过 Telegram 机器人检查波场钱包地址是否在 USDT 合约的黑名单上。当用户通过 Telegram 机器人发送指令 {walletAddress} 时，工作流查询 Tronscan API 以确定提供的钱包地址是否被列入黑名单，然后通过 Telegram 机器人将结果发送回用户。
